body_html:
Hi @andrewginns Have you tried using your model with the TF Lite demo app? (Trying to find out if this affect only tensorflow for poets or not)

It looks like your model is OK and can run with benchmark_model, for example:

$ bazel run -c opt tensorflow/contrib/lite/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model -- --graph=`realpath ~/Downloads/float.tflite`

body:
Hi @andrewginns Have you tried using your model with the [TF Lite demo app](https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/tree/master/tensorflow/contrib/lite/java/demo/app)? (Trying to find out if this affect only tensorflow for poets or not)

It looks like your model is OK and can run with benchmark_model, for example:
```
$ bazel run -c opt tensorflow/contrib/lite/tools/benchmark:benchmark_model -- --graph=`realpath ~/Downloads/float.tflite`
```
